Posts.Content: Hi Chris, Seems we have sort of lost track of each other. Just checking in to see how you are doing?  Tomorrow I start my first round of chemo, I am getting 4 cycles. I have been informed that I will probably be sick after, so I have been given a script of compazine.  But for some weird reason I am have been feeling sort of sick to my stomach, the last 5 days.  hope you are doing well.   Barbz
